//output: ../index.html

extends ./layout.jade

block content
  section.projects.sheet
    article
      h1 Projects.
      table(width='', cellpadding='10')
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p Temere is a Latin word that means "by chance" this webapp a new tab buddy designed to greet you with an inspiring quote, dope shapes, and iconic backgrounds. I'm using Firebase + Facebook to create an interactive todo list you can access anywhere in the world. Set
                a(href="http://temere.herokuapp.com") Temere.space 
                | as your homepage and start to fly. 
            img(src="./assets/images/temere.space.jpg")
            h3
              span Temere.Space
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p Bckpckr is a hackathon proof of concept, built with ROR4 and designed to make your world backpacking experience simpler. Give us date's and location, we will give you the perfect itinerary. Just think of this as your best friend who always knows exactly where to take you!
            img(src="./assets/images/bckpckr.jpg")
            h3 
              span Bckpckr
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p A.IM is a Node.js application designed for car dealerships to have live tracking of their vehicles. Each vehicle has GPS tracking that sends its current location to the server.
              
            img(src="./assets/images/aim.jpg")
            h3 
              span Auto.Inventory Management
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p Project Spring Grove was a redesign of firstepisodeclinic.org both for the frontend as well as the backend architecture. Being the lead developer on this project was super exciting for me! I used PHP5, CSS3 (bootstrap), & HTML5
            img(src="./assets/images/psg.jpg")
            h3 
              span Project Spring Grove
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p While I interned at Mission Media I was able to take part in content creation, and design research for ojaswellness.com. I used cold fusion, PHP5, and Javascript to transform this page to something special.
            img(src="./assets/images/ojas.jpg")
            h3 
              span Ojas wellness
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p Geographic gram was the first thing I ever built at a hackathon. GeoGram essintally allow's you to see user images from all over the world with a simple place's search! I learned PHP, JS, HTML5/CSS3, Google Maps API, and Instagram API! 
            img(src="./assets/images/geogram.jpg")
            h3 
              span Geographic gram
   include ./includes/foot.jade
